'''Mel Gambôa''' (yavutse ku ya 23 Gicurasi 1984) ni umukinnyi wa filime w’umunyaromaniya utuye muri [[Angola]], umunyamakuru, na producer wa televiziyo.

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Gambôa yavutse 1984 i Bucharest, muri Rumaniya. <ref name="voa">https://www.voaportugues.com/a/angola-fala-so-bilhete-identidade-mel-gamboa/3026186.html</ref> Umukobwa wa se wa Angola na nyina w’umuromaniya, yatangiye gutaramira mu ikinamico mu 1998, yinjira mu itsinda ry’ikinamico Horizonte Nzinga Mbandi nk'igikorwa kidasanzwe. Hagati ya 2001 na 2003, Gambôa yabaga i Madrid maze yinjira mu itsinda ry’ikinamico Los Sobrinos del Mago de Oz nk'umukinnyi wa filime akaba n’umuyobozi wungirije w’imikino y’abana "El Gnomo Jeromo" na "Los Evangelios Apócrifos" na Frank Huesca. <ref name="mindelact">https://expressodasilhas.cv/cultura/2014/09/25/mindelact-a-orfa-do-rei-em-cena-hoje-a-noite/43073</ref>

Mu 2004, yasubiye i Luanda yitangira ikinamico, yitabira amahugurwa menshi kandi yiga amasomo y'ubuhanzi. Gambôa yinjiye muri societe yo muri iki gihe imbyino na percussion Manésema mu 2006 nk'umuyobozi ushinzwe imibanire rusange n’umuyobozi ushinzwe imihango. Mu 2007, yatangiye umwuga we kuri tereviziyo.  Mu mwaka wa 2010, Gambôa yashinze isosiyete ikorana na Multimedia Together Now, usibye gutanga serivisi zo gufotora no gufata amashusho, yashyizeho gahunda zamahugurwa kubakinnyi n’amasomo ya "Photography Angola". <ref>http://www.angop.ao/angola/pt_pt/noticias/lazer-e-cultura/2015/10/47/Angola-Aberto-curso-fotografia,01f00406-fa54-4564-9f69-163d8e8e8ba2.html</ref>

Gambôa yabaye umuyobozi wa gahunda yimyidagaduro ''Tchilar kumuyoboro'' wa 2 wa Televiziyo rusange muri Angola. Muri 2012, yatangiye kwakira ikiganiro cya radio cyitwa ''Show da Mel'' kuri Rádio Despertar 91.0 FM. <ref name=":2">http://www.angonoticias.com/Artigos/item/33308/mel-gamboa-na-despertar</ref>

Muri 2017, Gambôa yimukiye i Los Angeles kugira ngo arangize amashuri ye muri sinema. Kubera ibibazo by'amafaranga, yahatiwe gukoresha imbuga nkoranyambaga kugira ngo yishakire inkunga. <ref>https://www.ongoma.news/artigo/dificuldades-financeiras-obrigam-mel-gamboa-a-pedir-ajuda-nas-redes-sociais</ref>

Gambôa ni umunyamurwango uharanira inyungu z'umugore kandi yavuze ko abaturage badashobora kumenya ibibera muri politiki ya Angola. <ref>https://www.voaportugues.com/a/angola-fala-so-mel-gamboa-feminista-louca-incomoda/3029446.html</ref> Yimenyereza tantra yoga no gufotora. Yize ibitabo bivuga ku idini ry'Ababuda. 

